com.synergix.utilities

Class SessionData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.synergix.utilities.SessionData

  • public class SessionData
extends Object
    Table data, Excel data utility for data table of cucumber feature file and CRUD from Excel File(.xls only) for using in everywhere of FW. WARNING: for more performance and easy to maintain data, please follow the rule: 1. All column data must have unique name 2. Header Data ranger in each sheet must be defined(Example : Set format to text) and not empty 3. Key File Name must be unique.
    Author:
    Vincent
